{"tid":1288667,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【呼籲義工】PP對出小小的紀念地方","createTime":"2019-07-05T17:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T09:45:58.000Z","uid":67069,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"af64e241ca6e577ae6af273d99ae67e6b76b3d65","tid":1288667,"uid":67069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人轉過過黎，不過睇到而有時間既朋友都可以去幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【代轉】<br />\n太古金鐘(PP)對出還有個小小的紀念地方，<br />\n朋友協助了外籍記者訪問看守的婆婆，<br />\n訪問完了問婆婆有什麼可以幫手。<br />\n她說<ins><strong>三不五時有人扔玻璃瓶，偷祭品，指罵和打她</strong></ins>。婆婆不要金錢捐助，因此朋友只幫她買了包太平梳打餅，兩包鮮奶，3A電池(祭壇照明用品要用)。婆婆身體不好，希望有心人幫忙顧花，因為如果啲花枯萎發臭惹蚊PP會不喜，百合花別摘掉花蕊因為能趕蚊。<ins>幫忙換花水</ins>，平放的花要<ins>灑鮮花素</ins>但唔知邊度買，<ins>一袋紙鶴要搵人幫手掛起佢</ins>。婆婆說不是要人保護她，只要有人顧顧花就好。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qoJgWW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qoJgWW.jpg&h=946ca10d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJVrZah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJVrZah.jpg&h=7a639091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdAogWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjdAogWY.jpg&h=c2951398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkALvgZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkALvgZ.jpg&h=a1101caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yppMeJF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyppMeJF.jpg&h=0165dc82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWy5vg1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWy5vg1.jpg&h=6ca05806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家幫幫手</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810daf546945ca275e27c9e8c74ea2be5ee42860","tid":1288667,"uid":38055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:28:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a75b4bbaa52cb626fb12794948f3747397f2979a","tid":1288667,"uid":205778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:29:04.000Z","msg":"Pish <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uz63gZh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUz63gZh.gif&h=82ba5bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFPXmqX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFPXmqX.png&h=5186a4d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53f61b92c3ea677e65f9fec2caab8b74b01b45d5","tid":1288667,"uid":138482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b0e92e43f5b9cb856d57f2a99543abda6c1ad0","tid":1288667,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:30:07.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"a39aeb5539339a83a47474497cdd8aba0c9b3d13","tid":1288667,"uid":235796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:30:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d553fafd6ec1815ca7f8bca9a614d438b7d229c","tid":1288667,"uid":178791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b78d13f33935d338d31666911e0ba7c6708d1509","tid":1288667,"uid":74272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:31:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e5027a1333a5519fc426ea826726568c244b134","tid":1288667,"uid":247483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:35:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"0ae662e8483d09454f6f72dbc638f719982d9ede","tid":1288667,"uid":268623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:39:24.000Z","msg":"個婆婆真係好有心"},{"pid":"371be194f2aa793a75ee